_sText:
Prefab: The prefab includes a Maze with aimtextures...
And on every death 'road' you can find a 'funny' CS:S 'Spray'.

The maze is protected for 'roof' runners so they can't jump on it.

I don't know if somebody can use this prefab, but it's an old one, made when i started mapping...

So enjoy ;)

You don't need to credit me, but if you do, big hug :D

Note: it was originally made for a new gungame map, but i've never finished it...
